* 早上有數千人在[[自由广场_(华盛顿哥伦比亚特区)|自由廣場]]聚集準備參與在特區的示威活動<ref name=FreedomPlaza5564>{{Cite web|last=Ramirez|first=Stephanie|date=2021-01-05|title=Several arrested on gun charges as pro-Trump rallies begin in DC|url=https://www.fox5dc.com/news/several-arrested-on-gun-charges-as-pro-trump-rallies-begin-in-dc|access-date=2021-01-07|website=FOX 5 DC|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107005621/https://www.fox5dc.com/news/several-arrested-on-gun-charges-as-pro-trump-rallies-begin-in-dc|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*眾議員[[佐伊·洛夫格伦|佐伊·洛夫格伦]]（民·[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]）與國會警察局局長桑德及眾議院警衛官歐文舉行電話會議。桑德告知洛夫格伦[[美國國民警衛隊|國民警衛隊]]已經整裝待命，國會警方亦有充足警力應對示威活動<ref name="wp-inside-siege-demirjian">{{cite news |last1=Demirjian |first1=Karoun |last2=Leonnig |first2=Carol D. |last3=Kane |first3=Paul |last4=Davis |first4=Aaron C. |title=Inside the Capitol siege: How barricaded lawmakers and aides sounded urgent pleas for help as police lost control |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/inside-capitol-siege/2021/01/09/e3ad3274-5283-11eb-bda4-615aaefd0555_story.html |access-date=2021-01-09 |work=The Washington Post |date=2021-01-09 |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110032733/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/inside-capitol-siege/2021/01/09/e3ad3274-5283-11eb-bda4-615aaefd0555_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
**桑德向洛夫格伦匯報完後另外向眾議員[[提姆·瑞安|提姆·瑞安]]（民·[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]]）重申國會警方已經準備就緒<ref name="wp-inside-siege-demirjian" />。
*晚上至翌日上午，至少10人被捕，部分人被捕理由為持有武器<ref name="McEvoy-Forbes">{{Cite web|last=McEvoy|first=Jemima|date=2021-01-06|title=DC Protests Live Coverage: Entire Capitol Now On Lockdown As Protesters Enter The Building|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/jemimamcevoy/2021/01/06/dc-protests-trump-pro-trump-rally-live-coverage/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106200617/https://www.forbes.com/sites/jemimamcevoy/2021/01/06/dc-protests-trump-pro-trump-rally-live-coverage/|archive-date=2021-01-06|access-date=2021-01-06|website=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

